originalText.text:
Auntie Gwen’s daycare allows parents to go to work with a great since of confidence and comfortability knowing   that your child is in a safe, nurturing and stimulating environment. She and her loving staff  have cared for my son since the age of 16 months old. This fall of 2021 he will go onto pre-K. I can not reiterate how more than prepared he is for his next educational journey . He can identify all of his Letters , numbers , colors , animals and more.  The list can honestly go and on. Plus he can read and write  at 3 years old! Mrs. Gwen is a highly skilled professional with the ability to teach your child through their milestones. You will not find a caregiver more accommodating and caring for
Your child care needs.
